metadata.metaValue:
This is the compound that
- converts any array to strings
- tells us the type
- creates an info string for this array type (e.g. "Min/Max")

So far these types are supported:
- float, double
- vector2, 3, 4
- char, short, int, long, and their unsigned
- bool
- string
- matrix4x4
- object shows just the type

If you want to print info for other types then add them
 in this compound.

If you want more/other info strings then edit this compound
